title: Doctor Who Revisited - the Eleventh Doctor
description:
This is the Eleventh Doctor Revisited, in mp4 and 720p.

Can't believe we've reached the end. Is the Twelfth Doctor Revisited next month? The War Doctor Revisited? How about the Brigadier Revisited? Or Sarah Jane? I'd be down for the Curator Revisited myself.

Gotta see Day of the Doctor in 3D at the cinema tonight. Debating whether to wear THE SCARF or not...
